entries.femaleVariant: Nothin'... just that corporat-fuck that ran over my daughter – saw it with my own eyes, but... he pays every month. Pays a lot...
He'll pay when you redecorate the highway with his fuckin' brains...

<mothertongue l="mex" m="Mira" b="" a=", if I kill him or sell him out to the badges, I won't make the rent. Besides, the <Rich color=\"MainColors.ActiveBlue\">pinche cabrón</>has connections to Grove Street."/>
You think that's what Lisa would've wanted? Revenge? She wasn't like that...
Papi, you're killin' me. Fuck the eddies. Be a man and drag that piece o' dog shit 'round the streets for everyone to see.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="¡nomás hazlo!" b="You mean 6th Street? See? You're gettin' everythin' mixed up now! Don't overthink this – " a=""/>
